Memo for the National Guard.1. Arrest all bank accounts associated with the organization of the demonstration.2. Block the demonstration perimeter.3. Twice offer to disperse and, spraying gas, begin to pack the demonstrators.4. In the presence of "their children" write out to parents a fine and / or up to five years in prison.5. Write down the fact of throwing anything at the police - after that, the use of special equipment becomes democratic, regardless of the time of throwing objects at the police. Regards, Canadian police.